Description
==================================

Hack The Game is a hacking
simulator. It gives you a taste of
very basic hacking.

==================================
Details
==================================

Version: 1.21
Size: 2.44MB (uncompressed)

==================================
Installation/Play
==================================

To play, just run
"Hack The Game.exe" and enter your
hacker name, then choose the
mission pack you would like to do.
